  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个用户行为追踪系统，核心目标是检测异常登录和账号共享。整个流程要分成四个阶段：数据采集、实时摄入、图分析、最后实时阻断。先从Stage1开始，有两个数据源。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Stage1",
        "ValidationSvc",
        "BookstoreSvc"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。Stage1是实时采集层。ValidationSvc和BookstoreSvc这两个服务具体采集什么字段？我需要确认数据语义才能确定下游关联逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ValidationSvc",
        "BookstoreSvc"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ValidationSvc采集IP、token、请求端点和查询参数；BookstoreSvc采集用户行为，关键是带上email标识。这两个服务独立部署，数据格式也不一样。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ValidationSvc",
        "BookstoreSvc",
        "IP",
        "token",
        "email"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在Stage1子图里画好了这两个服务，标注了各自捕获的字段。接下来它们怎么流转？直接写库还是先过消息队列削峰？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Stage1",
        "ValidationSvc",
        "BookstoreSvc"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "必须过Kafka。ValidationSvc发到naglfar-validation-topic，存请求元数据；BookstoreSvc发到naglfar-user-journey-topic，存用户行为。两个topic分开，消费端可以灵活订阅。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Kafka",
        "ValidationTopic",
        "JourneyTopic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：两个服务都是Publish到Kafka，延迟要求小于5毫秒对吧？我在边上标注了这个SLA。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ValidationSvc",
        "BookstoreSvc",
        "ValidationTopic",
        "JourneyTopic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，5毫秒内必须发出，不能阻塞主流程。现在看Stage2，需要一个Worker同时消费这两个topic，做数据清洗和关联。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Stage2",
        "Worker",
        "ValidationTopic",
        "JourneyTopic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Worker的技术栈有要求吗？还有，enrich具体做什么？是把IP解析成地理位置，还是把token关联到账号ID？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Worker",
        "Stage2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "用.NET写，叫Naglfar Worker。enrich包括补全账号信息、解析设备指纹，还有关键的一步：把ValidationTopic和JourneyTopic的事件按时间窗口关联，比如同一个token在5秒内既有验证请求又有购书行为。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Worker",
        "Stage2",
        "ValidationTopic",
        "JourneyTopic",
        "token"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Stage2画好了，标注了near real-time小于1秒的延迟。Worker同时consume两个topic。下一步数据存哪里？需要支持复杂关系查询。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Stage2",
        "Worker",
        "ValidationTopic",
        "JourneyTopic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "存Neo4j。节点类型有IP、Token、Account、Request、Action五种，关系包括MADE_REQUEST、USED_TOKEN这些。图结构才能做后续的旅程关联分析。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Storage",
