      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Worker到Neo4j的写入延迟要控制在1秒内？我在箭头上标注了。现在Stage3是分析层，batch还是streaming模式？",
      "elements_involved": [
